Text:
Sorry, gave up on making it look nice after ThePirateBay refused my first few (much prettier) attempts to submit it. 
And I forgot to put "Enjoy!" at the end. ~_^.
Excellent. Thanks a lot. The audio quality is fine. No problems at all. And it's a good book. I'd love to see more true crime audiobooks on Pirate Bay :)
No problem, and it's nice to hear that my experimenting with methods for the best sound is appreciated :) . (I rather enjoyed the book as well too; especially since it also has functional value)
